com.google.cloud.compute.deprecated

Class NetworkInterface

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.cloud.compute.deprecated.NetworkInterface
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class NetworkInterface
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A network interface for a Google Compute Engine instance. Network interfaces specify how the instance is configured to interact with other network services, such as connecting to the internet.
    See Also:
    Configuring an Instance's IP Addresses, Serialized Form
